\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pi(x)\sim\frac{x}{\log x}.
\]

\end_inset

The notation 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)\sim g(x)$
\end_inset

 means 
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{x\to\infty}f(x)/g(x)=1$
\end_inset

